config.path: the path where your main class is found (ex : com/your/path.java)
config.exportname: export name of your mod (ex. modid-1.0.jar (you can find this by going into your build.gradle file and checking the 'archivesBaseName', by default it is modid-1.0.jar))
config.line: the line of code where your webhook is expected
config.stringname: the name of the string where your webhook is expected (ex : String -> WEBHOOK = 'webhook here';)
